ca.peterzhu.basestation.dao.bean

Class BaseStationBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.peterzhu.basestation.dao.bean.BaseStationBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Named(value="baseStationBean")
 @ConversationScoped
public class BaseStationBean
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Contains all the the fields to represent a Base Station. This is a managed bean using CDI to interact with the JSF frontend.
    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Peter Zhu
    See Also:
